tent/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_boat_Margot_Robbie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>格蕾塔·葛韦格饰演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>芭比娃娃</em></a>在上映后在多个国家被禁。</p><p>这部由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/margot-robbie">玛格特·罗比</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-gosling">瑞恩·高斯林</a>主演的奇幻喜剧已成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-are-highest-grossing-movies-2023-3478504">2023 年全球第二高票房电影</a>，仅次于<em>《超级马里奥兄弟大电影》</em> ，本月初票房突破 10 亿美元大关。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">《芭比娃娃》评论：格蕾塔·葛韦格的成人玩具故事非常有趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部电影的成功也跨越了另一个里程碑，成为票房最高的完全由女性导演的真人电影。</p><h2><em>芭比</em>在哪里被禁止了？</h2><p>在 7 月份上映之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barbie-banned-in-vietnam-over-offending-south-china-sea-map-3464538"><em>《芭比娃娃》</em>在越南被禁</a>，因为其中的一个场景是描绘中国在南海有争议的领土主张的地图。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/barbie-movie-banned-vietnam-map-south-china-sea-rcna92314" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>路透社</em></a>报道，这一场景展示了“九段线”的“令人反感的图像”，中国地图上用这条线来说明其对南海大片地区的主权主张，越南对南海有争议。 </p><figure id="attachment_3470023" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3470023" style="width: 1615px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3470023" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530.jpg" alt="芭比" width="1615" height="1030" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530.jpg 1615w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-400x255.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-800x510.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-696x444.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-1392x888.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-1068x681.jpg 1068w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-300x191.jpg 300w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-768x490.jpg 768w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Robbie_Gosling-e1690467966530-1536x980.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3470023" class="wp-caption-text">瑞恩·高斯林和玛格特·罗比在《芭比娃娃》中。图片来源：华纳兄弟。</figcaption></figure><p>最近，许多电影因同样的原因在该国被禁，包括索尼的<em>《神秘海域》</em>和梦工厂的动画电影<em>《雪人奇缘》</em> 。</p><p>科威特<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/08/10/arts/barbie-ban-kuwait-lebanon.html#:~:text=Although%20the%20%E2%80%9CBarbie%E2%80%9D%20movie%20is%20a%20billion-dollar%20global,feature%20any%20scenes%20that%20overtly%20portray%20same-sex%20relationships." target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>新闻</em></a>出版部副部长拉菲·阿尔苏贝埃 (Lafy Al-Subei&#39;e) 表示，由于<em>芭比娃娃</em>宣传了“与科威特社会和公共秩序格格不入的思想和信仰”，科威特随后禁止了该片的上映。 <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/08/10/arts/barbie-ban-kuwait-lebanon.html#:~:text=Although%20the%20%E2%80%9CBarbie%E2%80%9D%20movie%20is%20a%20billion-dollar%20global,feature%20any%20scenes%20that%20overtly%20portray%20same-sex%20relationships." target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>约克时报</em></a>）。</p><p>大约在同一时间（8月9日），黎巴嫩文化部长穆罕默德·莫尔塔达（Mohammad Mortada）采取行动禁止<em>芭比娃娃</em>，称这部电影被发现“宣扬同性恋和性转变”。在莫塔达的声明中，他还表示，这部电影降低了家庭单位的重要性，“与信仰和道德价值观相矛盾”（来自<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2023/aug/09/lebanon-in-move-to-ban-barbie-film-for-promoting-homosexuality" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>路透社</em></a>）。</p><p>据官方消息人士和当地 24H Algerie 新闻网站（ <a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/algeria-bans-barbie-movie-media-official-source-say-2023-08-14/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>路透社</em></a>）报道，阿尔及利亚<em>在芭比娃娃</em>在该国发行三周后就对其进行了禁止，理由是它“宣扬同性恋和其他西方越轨行为”。</p><p>华纳兄弟尚未对禁令做出回应。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">四星评论</a>中写道：“接下来是一部细致入微、玫瑰色的喜剧冒险片，配以由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzo">Lizzo</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>主演的令人惊叹的流行配乐，不知怎的，它不辜负巨大的炒作。借用 Ken 最酷的夹克（在长长的阵容中）的双关语，<em>芭比</em>不仅仅是‘足够’。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-every-country-barbie-banned-3483447">《这里是所有禁止“芭比娃娃”的国家》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
